<chapter line="1">2. Akusalapeyyālaṃ</chapter>
<paragraph line="2" number="191-200"> Dukkhassa vaḍḍhi etesanti <bold>dukkhavaḍḍhikā</bold>. Ye hi dukkhaṃ vaḍḍhenti, punappunaṃ uppādenti, dukkhassa vaḍḍhi tesaṃ atthīti evaṃ vuttaṃ. <bold>Sukhavaḍḍhikā</bold>ti etthāpi eseva nayo.</paragraph>
